name: Among White Daisies
description: Among White Daisies is a voxel-art collection of 128 pieces in which artworks are based on a common scene with multiple variations. The artworks are semi-unique, closer to 1/1s and owners get beautiful twitter banners. There is scarcity and the collection family is scalable for different scenes. Rendered in Magicavoxel and post-processed with vintage filters.
